Defendant Paul Christopher Falkowski in court with attorney Steven C. McGaver.  Kevin M. Osborne appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Case called for plea and sentencing hearing. State files amended information. Atty McGaver waives reading of amended information. Defendant enters a plea of no contest to Counts 1, 2, and 3 on amended information. Court performs plea colloquy and finds defendant guilty. State gives sentencing recommendations. Atty McGaver makes statements regarding sentencing. Defendant makes statements.

The Defendant was sentenced to the following:

6 MONTHS HUBER (41 Days credit) with standard release conditions. Defendant to report by 10/03/14 by 6:00 pm.

COSTS:  $243+ $200 DNA surcharge (to be paid as a condition of probation)
